     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PKYM    6
     C                     PARM           P@MODE  1
     C                     PARM           P@HIN1  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN2  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN3  2
      *
