     C                     Z-ADD0         U       20
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KH
     C                     Z-ADD0         @KS
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @KB
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @UK
